omization as there is a simple and easy editor that allows the user to drag and drop content anywhere on the site. In addition to its core website-building functionality, it can easily build an online store. Wix has 500 online-store templates and comes with some stock images. It provides a hopping cart with full functionality. It is a time and cost-saving option as it is a fully-hosted service and works with plenty of apps designed to support it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since it is primarily a website builder its eCommerce capabilities are limited. Once a website has been published on this platform, the template cannot be changed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>WooCommerce</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The base WooCommerce plugin, in addition to many extensions, is free and open-source. It is meant for setting up a store on a WordPress website. A business would need to pay a hosting fee to WordPress. So some technical knowledge is required for setting up this eCommerce website development platform. It comes as a free download and is highly customizable and flexible. It allows the user to pick preferred custom plug-ins, website themes, and payment gateway.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WooCommerce is user-friendly but obviously lacks dedicated customer service. The interface is clean and modern.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Get Started Now</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>eFrog specializes in identifying the primary needs of your business and then recommending the best-suited eCommerce website development platform. We help you with all your queries so that you can compare and pick the best.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Along with emerging eCommerce development platforms, 2020 is also going to witness the rise of new website design trends. Click <a href=\"http://www.efrog.com.au/blog/2019/11/11/the-top-9-website-designing-trends-shaping-2020/\">here</a> to read all about them and stay updated on what’s happening in the website design industry. Please do not hesitate to <a href=\"http://www.efrog.com.au/#contactForm\">contact us</a> for a free consultation, either for getting help with your eCommerce website design platform or for any other need.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '7 Best eCommerce Website Development Platforms in 2020 and Beyond', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '129-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-11-22 11:42:56', '2019-11-22 11:42:56', '', 129, 'http://www.efrog.com.au/blog/2019/11/22/129-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
